block.cyber_rewared.blueprint_archive.tt:
Stores Cyberware Blueprints.
Accessible by Engineering Table if adjacent.
block.cyber_rewared.charger.ttp:
Charges entities with Cyberware.
Accepts TR Energy.
block.cyber_rewared.component_box.ttp:
Stores Components.
Accessible by Engineering Table if adjacent.
block.cyber_rewared.engineering_table.tt: Used to dismantle and create Cyberware.
block.cyber_rewared.radio_post.ttp:
Constructs a large Radio.
To form:
  - Place 4 layers of 3x3 components. (3x4x3)
  - 6 layers of a single component, centered
    over the base.
block.cyber_rewared.robosurgeon.ttp:
Used to set what Cyberware to install or remove.
Place on top of a Surgery Chamber to use.
block.cyber_rewared.surgery_chamber.ttp:
Performs Operations for the Robosurgeon.
Right-click while inside to activate .
config.cyber_rewared.option.critical_ess: Threshold below which you will take damage and require Anti-Rejection shots.
config.cyber_rewared.option.cyberentitie:
If true, Cyberentities like the Cyberzombie will be able to replace their
Default counterpart.
config.cyber_rewared.option.cyberzombie_: Base chance for a cyberzombie to replace a normal zombie
config.cyber_rewared.option.engineering_:
Chance to get a blueprint when smashing a Cyberitem
in an Engineering Table.
config.cyber_rewared.option.katana_enabl:
If true, Katana is enabled and can be obtained,
if false, Katana is not obtainable
§cWARNING: THIS WILL ALSO REMOVE EVERY KATANA FROM
§cEVERY INVENTORY ONCE YOU LOAD A WORLD
config.cyber_rewared.option.natural_brut: Chance to spawn a Brute instead of a normal Cyberzombie.
